title: Catherine Cortez Masto Defended Her Nevada Seat, Winning Election to a Second Term
description: The victory by Senator Catherine Cortez Masto, Democrats’ most endangered incumbent, denies Republicans the chance to capture power in the chamber.
dc:creator: Catie Edmondson
media:description: Senator Catherine Cortez Masto of Nevada in Las Vegas last month. She is the nation’s first and only Latina senator.
